    • overlaps

      boolean overlaps(WC_PD_LimitsDelegate other)
      Checks if this partial disability benefit range overlaps with another one of the same type. In general no two items of the same type should overlap as we want to be able to look up just a single item when calculating benefits.
      Parameters:
      other - the other WC_PD_LimitsDelegate
      Returns:
      true if date ranges overlap, false otherwise
